oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performance by Suzy Bogguss and interview honoring Chet Atkins from the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on December 10, 2011. Companion to a Chet Atkins exhibit. Band includes Harry Stinson and Charlie Chadwick.
